<div id="login-guide-banner" class="login-guide" style="display: none;">
    <div class="guide-content">
        <div class="guide-icon">⚠️</div>
        <!-- Changed icon to alert/info -->
        <div class="guide-text">
            <strong>카카오/이메일 인증 필독사항</strong>
            <p>
                1. 인증 완료 후 <strong>[확인]</strong>을 누르면
                카카오톡/브라우저에 머물 수 있습니다.<br />
                2. 이 경우, 사용자가 직접 <strong>[앱 전환]</strong>을 하여 <strong
                    >RadSafety 앱으로 돌아와야</strong
                > 로그인이 완료됩니다.<br />
                3. 앱으로 돌아오면 마이페이지가 보입니다.<br />
                4. 확인하셨다면 아래 <strong>[다시 보지 않기]</strong>를
                눌러주세요.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <button id="guide-close-btn" class="guide-btn"
        >이 내용을 이해했으며, 다시 보지 않기</button
    >
</div>

<style>
    .login-guide {
        /* Position: Relative to content or fixed near top? */
        /* User said "Development features start location", which is usually below the main buttons */
        /* Let's make it static/relative within the flow if possible, OR fixed but centered higher */
        /* DashboardLayout renders it at body bottom. Fixed positioning is safest to overlay. */

        position: fixed;
        top: 20%; /* Higher up */
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 400px;
        background: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #fee500; /* Kakao Border */
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        z-index: 2000; /* Very high priority */
        padding: 1.25rem;
        font-family:
            -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        text-align: left;
    }

    .guide-content {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .guide-icon {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .guide-text strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: #191919;
    }

    .guide-text p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
        word-break: keep-all; /* Korean optimized */
    }

    .guide-btn {
        width: 100%;
        background: #fee500;
        color: #191919;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .guide-btn:active {
        background: #e6cf00;
    }
</style>

<script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
        const guideBanner = document.getElementById("login-guide-banner");
        const closeBtn = document.getElementById("guide-close-btn");

        // Check if dismissed
        const isDismissed = localStorage.getItem("login_guide_dismissed");

        // Logic: Show ONLY on /login page
        const path = window.location.pathname;
        const shoudShow = !isDismissed && path === "/login";

        if (shoudShow && guideBanner) {
            guideBanner.style.display = "block";
        }

        closeBtn?.addEventListener("click", () => {
            if (guideBanner) guideBanner.style.display = "none";
            localStorage.setItem("login_guide_dismissed", "true");
        });
    });
</script>
